data.description: You don't want to miss this this freshly updated home in a great subdivision in coveted Blue Springs school district. Two story front to back split home features a large den, non-conforming bedroom or office, and a full bathroom at the entry level. A beautifully re-stained banister guides the stairway to the upper floor, where a family room, dining room, open plan kitchen with all stainless appliances, and three bedrooms await. Primary suite bathroom features two sinks and large walk in closet. Three car tandem garage, tankless water heater, reverse osmosis system and water softener, lots of storage, full privacy fenced rear yard, patio and newer roof.
